@node description
@title "Amiga Crossword Deluxe"

 
 @{bold "Amiga Crossword Deluxe"} is as you've probably noticed a crossword game.
 The game has the following features:

 * Supports the 'Across Lite' puzzle file format.
 
 * System-friendly user interface, runs on the workbench screen.

 * Freeware.

 Please let me know if you use this game.
 I've put a lot of work into this program and only continue its development
 if i get some feedback.
 You can @{"send a email or a postcard" link "author"} or register online on my homepage:
 http://www.cybercomm.nl/~coenradi

 On the site of Literate Software @{bold "http://www.litsoft.com"} you find a puzzle gallery 
 and links to other across lite puzzle web sites.

 

 
  
@endnode

@node requirements
@title "Requirements"
 

 @{bold "Requirements:"}

 Amiga Crossword Deluxe works on any Amiga with Workbench 3.0 or higher.
 The game requires the Reqtools.library 
 A screenmode of 640x480 or higher is recommended.


@endnode

@node install
@title "How to install??"


 @{bold "Installation:"}

 Use the installer script supplied with this game.  
 No files will be copied into your system directories.


 If you want to install it manually - just copy the ACD drawer wherever you want.


 To deinstall Crossword_Deluxe just delete the ACD drawer.

@endnode

@node spel
@title "How to play..."
 
 
 
 @{bold "Usage:"}

 You can start the game from the Workbench and Shell.
 If you start the game without puzzle parameters a requester will appear and ask for a puzzle.


 Click on a square to highlight the corresponding clue.
 Click on the square again to switch the direction.
 Click on an Across or Down clue to highlight the corresponding squares.
 Use the Backspace or Deletekey to erase letters.
 
 
 

@endnode


